<section id="1002J_S0010" variety="S0010">
<name>BRAKE CONTROL</name>
<ttl id="1002J_S0010_72V8M_T003J" variety="T003J">
<name>BRAKE ACTUATOR (for ADVICS Made)</name>
<para id="RM0000013P8003X" category="A" type-id="8000E" name-id="BC13W-02" from="200601">
<name>REASSEMBLY</name>
<subpara id="RM0000013P8003X_01" type-id="01" category="01">
<s-1 id="RM0000013P8003X_01_0001" proc-id="RM0250U___00000MK00000">
<ptxt>INSTALL BRAKE ACTUATOR BRACKET ASSEMBLY</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Install the actuator assembly to the brake actuator bracket assembly with the 2 nuts.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C133322" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<torque>
<torqueitem>
<t-value1>5.4</t-value1>
<t-value2>55</t-value2>
<t-value3>48</t-value3>
</torqueitem>
</torque>
<atten3>
<ptxt>Do not remove the hole plug before installing a new brake actuator because the brake actuator assembly is filled with brake fluid.</ptxt>
</atten3>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
</subpara>
</para>
</ttl>
